# NOTE #
> Mouse keybinds / shortcuts only work while the current widget is active (clicked on / hovered over)

Topbar: (Major WIP)
"ctrl+e" -> Export / Render (Broken)
"ctrl+s" -> Save Project (Not Implemented)
"ctrl+o" -> Open Project (Not Implemented)
"ctrl+n" ->  New Project (Not Implemented)

Playback:
"p" -> Play/Pause playback


Media Manager: (WIP)
"ctrl+l" -> Load a new media object


Timelines:
"mousewheel" -> Move Left/Right on the timeline by 5 frames (@ 30fps)
"shift+mousewheel" -> Move Left/Right on the timeline by 60 frames (2s @30fps)

